69
00:09:13,804 --> 00:09:18,225
Pa, vaša majka nam je jutros
predocila nešto sasvim...

70
00:09:18,391 --> 00:09:20,936
Najbolje da prespavamo, pa onda...

71
00:09:21,102 --> 00:09:22,938
Ponovo cemo se sresti, zar ne?

72
00:09:23,104 --> 00:09:25,565
- cekacu napolju. Hvala, Jean.

73
00:09:25,649 --> 00:09:27,609
- Sedi, Simon.

74
00:09:27,734 --> 00:09:30,445
- Gledaj, Jean...

75
00:09:30,612 --> 00:09:33,281
