128
00:13:08,163 --> 00:13:09,664
- Dobar dan!

129
00:13:12,918 --> 00:13:15,712
Mi cemo poceti sa Sirakuzinom hipotezom.

130
00:13:18,548 --> 00:13:21,009
- Šta ti govori tvoja intuicija?

131
00:13:28,141 --> 00:13:30,018
Tvoji predosecaji su uvek u pravu.

132
00:13:30,185 --> 00:13:32,395
Zato i imaš potencijal

133
00:13:32,521 --> 00:13:34,940
da postaneš pravi matematicar.

134
00:13:35,065 --> 00:13:37,692
Ali ovde ce ti biti potrebna pomoc.

135
00:13:38,860 --> 00:13:40,862
Imaš li nekog od porodice tamo?

136
00:13:42,405 --> 00:13:45,075
Kontakte?
- To je besmisleno, Niv.

137
00:13:45,200 --> 00:13:48,745
- Upravo si saznala,
pod A, da ti je otac živ;

138
00:13:48,870 --> 00:13:50,956
i pod B, da imaš drugog brata.

139
00:13:51,081 --> 00:13:52,290
Kolko god bilo besmisleno,

140
00:13:52,290 --> 00:13:55,669
ti to neizbežno moraš da ispitaš.

141
00:13:55,794 --> 00:13:57,295
Ti moraš da znaš.

142
00:13:58,296 --> 00:14:00,966
U suprotnom, tvoj um nikada nece imati mira.

143
00:14:02,968 --> 00:14:06,638
A gde misli nisu mirne nema ciste matematike.

144
00:14:10,267 --> 00:14:12,352
To te dovodi na polaznu tacku.

145
00:14:18,066 --> 00:14:20,402
- Moj otac je umro tokom rata, u Dareshu.

146
00:14:20,569 --> 00:14:22,779
- To je nepoznata promenljiva jednacine.

147
