149
00:14:29,911 --> 00:14:31,746
koje se zove Der Om,
de Fouad.

150
00:14:32,998 --> 00:14:35,250
Studirala je francuski jezik

151
00:14:35,417 --> 00:14:36,751
na univerzitetu u Dareshu.

152
00:14:36,918 --> 00:14:39,838
- Ako je tamo studirala,
postoji nada.

153
00:14:41,423 --> 00:14:43,925
