Šta se dogodilo?

164
00:18:35,282 --> 00:18:36,700
Gde je Jeanne?

165
00:18:39,703 --> 00:18:41,204
Mama?

166
00:18:53,717 --> 00:18:55,427
- Da li ona pati od migrene?

167
00:18:55,552 --> 00:18:56,678
- Ne.

168
00:18:56,678 --> 00:18:58,847
- Gubitak pamcenja?
- Ne.

169
00:18:58,972 --> 00:19:01,099
- Gubitak ravnoteže?

170
00:19:01,266 --> 00:19:02,434
- Ne.

171
00:19:02,434 --> 00:19:04,019
- Privremena odsutnost?

